                <head>[Untitled]</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Colon</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1903-11-06T09:15:00-05:19">
                            <hi rend="italic">November 6, 1903, 9.15 a.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p rend="flushleft">
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Secretary of the Navy</hi>, <hi rend="italic">Washington,
                        D. C.:</hi>
                </p>
                <p>Arrived Thursday evening; landed force. Following conditions prevailing: Just
                    before landing all the troops of Colombia have left for R. M. S. P. Company’s
                    steamer <hi rend="italic">Orinoco</hi> for Cartagena. Independent party in
                    possession of Colon, Panama, and railroad line. <hi rend="italic">Nashville</hi>
                    withdrawn force.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Delano.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
